<node id="DIVIDEND DISTRIBUTION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Dividend Distribution is a significant factor affecting the company's shareholder equity and cash flow, as it impacts net profit and contributes to shareholder returns. Several companies have distributed dividends as part of their corporate governance strategy, including Acme Government Solutions distributing $5 million in January 2021, Buildcorp Holdings allocating £10 million in August 2018, Energex Corporation distributing dividends reflecting their commitment to returning value to investors, and JetWing Aviation distributing $10 million in August 2021. Innovate Tech Solutions declared a dividend distribution of $5 million in December 2017, reinforcing its commitment to long-term value creation. CleanCo decided to distribute $2 million in dividends in December, enhancing shareholder returns. MediaCorp has consistently distributed dividends to shareholders, rewarding them based on financial performance and improving investor confidence. Retail Emporia distributed $50 million in dividends to shareholders in October 2021, while HealthLife Solutions' distribution of dividends affects its shareholder equity.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-649bd1884762aea2938b30832b8e8be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5640965e12a7d1c1ece0ccd5e52e8285&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-afbb9d96222fae20455c239f73321bd0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92e86b7863a865759a972bf51c43af74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dc8d232e2d371fa082e7836970a64f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98a43bd74ef2a847668d6640a68904ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bca8ec9d1d6e3e0aad5d056e9866194e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82ba4c539815a0a9f46bb11576a3f1ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cafe4a3b179e06ea54279570fa2eeef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55c20f91ba49a43229335e5bc34ae99a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-150abd9008516086d5b2366f7fb78f0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-633d21efa8476cca47a49a179fb05ece&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f7e644c11cb2e56b59700ebf089a171&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce4e95fbf2152263ed3fef9699018408&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b1dc2b550b5abdbc1e17f5f37ab8571&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bc3f0fc44d1e5b7b92e36253c0960c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2cb16504e5422902fc9161b6ee2b5aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-559aced4edd7cd7f6687659b6c1456e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895f7a7ab99b8e763c26c240f54faa37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e66f373aca6a580de891440bbaec732&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1366a002d04d0be20cc1fe928f92adee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6de5a3c0778130c48d2a33144359a5fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12beac72bff5168206050a9b609ded89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e377246f7a1dcc16554baf0619938db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94c0ff6e8a42021239bed91389981361&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1bba366df3e6cede332c5f8161534e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce6fb42fcaf61dc0c4550dd1c02ce057&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e863ed97b54c4fcc9ab76db023dc0f36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2d9cd1f0d0f5c88cc1b20fb7c1e34f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-880b68e0207eb8871283226f78c6b7e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b10a8d4e350b5ba0e4f1ea3b1499c0a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fda519aa5fee272b7966c5763ada8208&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48c74faa9ee46dde4d587cb4b67464d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a554dcacbbbf8ca6a38364ecaf904a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3083d00fd8d7ee83dbaf7833322bcc4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f925d452424fe50f26f4d243b03a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-743fb1e0f6de8ce5694fbeb4ac080e79&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa45ec0a694715611913df6470ca8b86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8fa0741657950615e4107e53fd7c69b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06403e9ce7eae128e778e6a0a8af28bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88cc8320f1a79141f