<node id="GOVERNMENT CONTRACT">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Acme Government Solutions acquired a major government contract in March 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;Acme Government Solutions announced a new $100 million government contract.&lt;SEP&gt;Acme Government Solutions' announcement of a new $100 million government contract.</data>
