<node id="DEBT RESTRUCTURING">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt restructuring is a process where companies reorganize or renegotiate the terms of their outstanding debts to manage financial obligations more effectively. This strategy has been implemented across various entities such as StrongBuild Construction, JetWing Aviation, Green Fields Agriculture Co., ABC Education Corporation, Buildcorp Holdings, HealthLife Solutions, Sunrise Holidays, InnovaTech, Elevate Retail Inc., Acme Government Solutions, Energex, CleanCo, MediaCorp, InnovateTech Solutions, Stellar Entertainment, and Capital Finance Group. The main goal of debt restructuring is to optimize the capital structure, improve financial condition, reduce liabilities, and enhance overall financial stability.

In February 2018, Green Fields Agriculture Co. undertook a strategic move to restructure its debts and optimize its capital structure. In August 2021, HealthLife Solutions reduced its liabilities by $25 million as part of their debt restructuring process. Elevate Retail Inc. underwent debt restructuring in August 2020, reducing liabilities by $15 million. Acme Government Solutions also underwent debt restructuring in December 2021 to reduce liabilities by $20 million and improve financial efficiency.

InnovateTech Solutions reduced liabilities by $5 million in June 2021, while CleanCo had its liabilities reduced by $5 million during the same month. MediaCorp optimized its capital structure by reducing liabilities by $20 million in July. Stellar Entertainment underwent debt restructuring with a significant reduction of $100 million in May 2017. Capital Finance Group also reduced its liabilities by $100 million in November 2018.

Debt restructuring, as seen across these entities, involves renegotiating or reorganizing the terms of outstanding debts to manage financial obligations effectively and improve overall financial stability.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-649bd1884762aea2938b30832b8e8be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9ba7a3c0c8a9ce5c74c05489024ac8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55c20f91ba49a43229335e5bc34ae99a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da3dfc44e0e20a361eb045db7e22628c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c9069665681980c34f0c5f91f47d66f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5633f22fb1b1c1ecee2267da752e683&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fc8569fc33e5622067435f888d85568&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0bdc34ab00774b418d0dadf8c08b2bee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d89db1088d92f24c9800329e845aeadb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffb223d3c90febe60178e61b88c9cb64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6abf2d1e5e0859b55198459388dbec6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-481ea9dc5d369e95dee54308a182382b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcbb3f4073b439af37c7b3f41c7731e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18356a999935fc73cd0c452951d6eeef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12beac72bff5168206050a9b609ded89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4d08f086df92502ce292b25913ab9d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de6f0bd772823e972b8ed8802c4dbf62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a4222bc66dfe2fb664b84babef953a4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafb344f291f9e473efe96beee5b7b24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e863ed97b54c4fcc9ab76db023dc0f36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a7e75697f3fe5494f88f91818d4f947&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76a8a3b07647817dc111d70302c928c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5fdbb05ac262b69b16c82df8838d7b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e91802d4bb262d05d2be006ab28b38c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff59ef3f3a5b9bdfdfe4ff59c178d73f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae5acb2ae8cb461295e99fb9a61c4e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a554dcacbbbf8ca6a38364ecaf904a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-647d62f0e536c4c2ad925b3c9fe903c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25af743e23bbbb0b88d4e257a4e0f138&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44ca535efb5426210ce1fab3c5223445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95d9020c0f098b0ff5e53483c8097370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d50353c95a093a831c5d1c09de02080&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ded02a78b3d2cb63c1c063482a24a034&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-304dc2c6fe4dbb6da5e8de7ab2abd682&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02612be98eb47e7c447b68251dcb5880&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3aca3568309a845f7609c9511ac0b07d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ffa567b71abb486e21bdc327ee75241a</data>
