<node id="SHAREHOLDER EQUITY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Shareholder equity is the residual interest in the assets of a company after deducting liabilities, representing ownership value and total equity belonging to shareholders at the end of the accounting period. It can be influenced by net profit, dividend distribution, and capital reserves. The amount held by shareholders directly reflects their stake in the business. In various instances across different companies such as Stellar Entertainment, Hudson Consumer Goods Co., SkyQuest Airlines, and InnovaTech Solutions, shareholder equity ranged from $70 million to $3.5 billion or even £5,500,000. A strong shareholder equity demonstrates financial stability, while fluctuations may indicate changes in the company's performance or financial activities.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1d6be261e4848e6d88fcc8f2853b1a0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6768652b607739b4868c2e2e94cbd9de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-96bc4acfa99b76cb670ac74cb775f2ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6550f4ab83873cfa0c5ed39c79f14a8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d698132e0847656e006c12b1eaabb7df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-353d7acf7282812b3fbc45585b2a7680&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8a217ef4eafc34ecc28257e6c124669&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c968d198d0f7bfe01bedf3567c594b67&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-424a01882b17412003d1a002645ec307&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ab0a6d3baa75175f2cb9d33eb5e0d56&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5133e5f2fd63fa53e6344e39ce74efd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-880b68e0207eb8871283226f78c6b7e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae5acb2ae8cb461295e99fb9a61c4e52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0c64b50954665c425fa1322725ace6f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63b9f3875f971b6c285ab4779dfdda99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33f925d452424fe50f26f4d243b03a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8105a2621d49530c5fc80333fd22b12&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c688214caf3d584102aa40f0eb0e761&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0007b179cc06d4425f838773e5e14956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b4529c5f071f63d611b81d5299fc5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a113b0909c2dac524300647678d8f5ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8fa0741657950615e4107e53fd7c69b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1eb124b2279c03c2b75916b6db3c8e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-647d62f0e536c4c2ad925b3c9fe903c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8c4fe74cb35c08bbd935e49c06e959&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3eeea6791b5a14e0e08a53ed1810132d</data>
