<node id="DEBT RATIO">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt Ratio is a financial metric that measures a company's leverage by dividing its total liabilities by total assets. This ratio indicates the proportion of debt relative to total assets and provides insight into the level of financial risk associated with the company. A value of 40% represents a balanced level of debt, while values above or below this range indicate higher or lower levels of financial risk respectively. The Debt Ratio is crucial for understanding a company's leverage position and its ability to meet its financial obligations in the long term. Companies such as Sunrise Holidays, Elevate Retail Inc., InnovateTech, Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc., GreenTech Solutions Inc., HealthLife Solutions, HealthPro Innovations, Hudson Consumer Goods Co., JetWing Aviation, MediaCorp, SkyQuest Airlines, EduCorp, and Entertainment Enterprises Inc. have been noted for their respective debt ratios of 53%, 39.58%, 40%, 0.375, 30%, 25%, 42%, 20%, 40%, 0.5, 42%, and 0.4 respectively. These values provide valuable insights into the financial stability and risk levels associated with each company.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bb0d2aa13cd58afc1600bbee4279a805&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-165d8b8b5dbfb1422521a68741ec638d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c03c13da62d2627b4b9e4d83e5d2efff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0aae5a177e9b1f725b29183a8fa7ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab52dad2f13037d52c7c74efd2b6abc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19356bb5dc15659ab30b035a2bf3a049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3351f71e7936625da48cf216c2382329&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72a1099c9983249a62d47c9ad9e93bb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd6ed115fb61e993235a40d9e448d2d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13d0df5ff1e00f9cc894f2ea3b78b815&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d698132e0847656e006c12b1eaabb7df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3eeea6791b5a14e0e08a53ed1810132d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0c64b50954665c425fa1322725ace6f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c79a7e06710255c4655d366464007a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b4529c5f071f63d611b81d5299fc5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c54f31f791748ed20ab5403c80946987&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10274b4ab21580cee6b676d4f2bfe1ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0eb2e27371cfc463f7b6c04a1c26315c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f7af81b796b51dbb60ceb68f358b34a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-546af81c8ff899be7e47fbf1b4210cc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8c4fe74cb35c08bbd935e49c06e959&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75dfc4f927c41b6e0c1b3add5242423c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-545d9fba32a712aefc0a29651c849f9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f1243deb9eb5e10a9f6d36db18a4d55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0eed546132b43d9e1543d288a4feb3c5</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 9}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 73}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 246}]</data>
</node>
<node id="DEBT TO ASSETS RATIO">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">The Debt-to-Assets Ratio is a financial indicator that measures the proportion of a company's assets financed by debt, where a value of 0.4 suggests moderate financial leverage. This ratio provides insight into a company's financial stability and risk level, as higher ratios indicate greater reliance on borrowed funds.

For instance, Acme Financial Services reported a Debt-to-Assets Ratio of 32.0%, indicating a moderate level of leverage in its operations. Similarly, Elevate Retail Inc., InnovateTech, Sunrise Holidays, MediaCorp, JetWing Aviation, Grand Adventures Tourism Ltd., and EduCorp all have debt-to-assets ratios ranging from 25% to 38%, suggesting balanced financial leverage.

In contrast, HealthPro Innovations had a Debt-to-Assets Ratio of 0.4 or 40%, indicating effective management of liabilities relative to its total assets. Meanwhile, Evergreen Consumer Goods Co. demonstrated effective management of liabilities with a debt-to-assets ratio of 38%.

Overall, these entities exhibit varying levels of financial leverage, influenced by their respective Debt-to-Assets Ratios.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-165d8b8b5dbfb1422521a68741ec638d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-354705f9fed355c46a465714c69ecd55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae82c3005de4fcc01d782bb2c876b9af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-572e1743afa8d92f3525e32e9e2669ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0aae5a177e9b1f725b29183a8fa7ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68b4593160d2ab215bbdf9039df29bf3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab52dad2f13037d52c7c74efd2b6abc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19356bb5dc15659ab30b035a2bf3a049&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3351f71e7936625da48cf216c2382329&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd6ed115fb61e993235a40d9e448d2d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13d0df5ff1e00f9cc894f2ea3b78b815&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d650d4bc162552af3a3e6ebb1556ffc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37a242b6195246f6844b4957c9d6bfd1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0c64b50954665c425fa1322725ace6f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c79a7e06710255c4655d366464007a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c54f31f791748ed20ab5403c80946987&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f7af81b796b51dbb60ceb68f358b34a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-546af81c8ff899be7e47fbf1b4210cc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-545d9fba32a712aefc0a29651c849f9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f56b150dcf1c213dfe1f09e6b357d358&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0eed546132b43d9e1543d288a4feb3c5</data>
