  <data key="d1">A governance body that supports the board of directors in overseeing company activities.&lt;SEP&gt;The Supervisory Board is another important governance entity at SkyQuest Airlines.&lt;SEP&gt;The Supervisory Board is another key governance entity in the organization, ensuring accountability and representation of shareholders' interests.&lt;SEP&gt;The Supervisory Board is another organizational body involved in the governance improvement plans at HealthLife Solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;The standing body that works alongside the Board of Directors in overseeing the operations and governance of Acme Government Solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;The supervisory board complements the board of directors in governing Vanguard Media Group.&lt;SEP&gt;The supervisory board works alongside the board of directors to ensure proper oversight.</data>
