<node id="RETURN ON EQUITY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A measure of financial performance measuring how efficiently a company generates profit from its shareholders' equity.&lt;SEP&gt;A metric that measures the efficiency of using shareholder equity to generate profits, where a value of 10% indicates efficient use.&lt;SEP&gt;A ratio that measures a company's operational efficiency based on shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Acme Financial Services' financial metric representing return on equity at 11.5%, indicating efficient use of shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;In 2019, National Development Corporation achieved a return on equity of 0.037.&lt;SEP&gt;MediaCorp's return on equity stood at 10%, demonstrating operational efficiency of shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Return on Equity (ROE) is a financial ratio calculated by dividing net profit by average shareholder equity, indicating operational efficiency based on shareholders' invested capital.&lt;SEP&gt;Return on Equity (ROE) is a financial ratio measuring operational efficiency based on net profit and shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Return on equity for Elevate Retail Inc., indicating operational efficiency.&lt;SEP&gt;Return on equity is a financial ratio that measures operational efficiency, calculated as net profit divided by average shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Return on equity measures operational efficiency, calculated at 18%, influenced by changes in net profit and shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;Sunrise Holidays achieved a return on equity of 17%, reflecting the efficiency of shareholder equity in generating profits.&lt;SEP&gt;Sunrise Holidays' return on equity was 17%, indicating the efficiency of shareholder equity in generating profits.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity for HealthPro Innovations was 13.33%, measuring operational efficiency based on shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity for SkyQuest Airlines was calculated at 11.4%, reflecting profitability relative to shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity for Sparkling Clean Housekeeping Services was calculated at 14.5%. This metric indicates how effectively the company generates returns from its shareholders' investments.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity for Stellar Entertainment in 2017 was calculated at 20%, reflecting operational efficiency relative to shareholders' equity.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity for the year was 16%, reflecting the operational efficiency of shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity measures the operational efficiency of shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity of 18% indicates the company's ability to generate profits from shareholders' investments.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity was 17%, indicating the operational efficiency of shareholder equity.</data>
