<node id="FINANCING ACTIVITY">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A large-scale financing activity conducted by Fabrikon Manufacturing Ltd. in August 2021 to raise $100 million for its expansion and development plans.&lt;SEP&gt;In February 2021, HealthPro Innovations conducted a large-scale financing activity raising $150 million to support its expansion and development.&lt;SEP&gt;In July 2017, Hudson Consumer Goods Co. conducted a financing activity involving raising $100 million through a bond issuance.&lt;SEP&gt;In March 2018, Buildcorp Holdings conducted a large-scale financing activity, raising £100 million from investors.&lt;SEP&gt;In March 2020, InnovateTech Solutions conducted a large-scale financing activity, raising $50 million of funds.&lt;SEP&gt;The company conducted a large-scale financing activity, raising $2.5 billion for future initiatives.&lt;SEP&gt;The company's large-scale financing activity in July raised $50 million of funds, strengthening its financial position.&lt;SEP&gt;The large-scale financing activity completed by AccuTech Solutions Inc. in October 2019 to raise funds for expansion and support plans.&lt;SEP&gt;The large-scale financing activity undertaken by Evergreen Consumer Goods Co. in March 2017, which strengthened their financial position.</data>
