<node id="SKYQUEST AIRLINES">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">SKYQUEST AIRLINES, a publicly traded full-service airline based in Palm City, Florida, offers both domestic and international flight services within the aviation industry. The company has focused on enhancing its financial strength for expansion by raising bonds. SkyQuest Airlines is committed to sustainability, environmental protection, social responsibility, community development projects, and responsible travel initiatives.

The company's governance structure impacts ethical practices, transparency, and accountability, reflected in the appointment of a Chief Integrity Officer and robust risk management strategies that integrate sustainable development and social responsibility principles into its operations. The airline emphasizes transparency and information disclosure to stakeholders while focusing on future growth plans such as fleet expansion, route development, and research investments.

SKYQUEST AIRLINES has implemented significant changes to strengthen internal controls, improve operational efficiency, and mitigate risks associated with financial performance in 2017, including the acquisition of WingsAway Airlines and Aerovia. The company also adopted new charters, expanded its operations through investments in aircraft maintenance facilities, and distributed dividends to shareholders.

The airline's focus on risk management includes a robust internal control system that prevents misconduct and detects fraudulent activities, while regulatory approvals from the FAA for long-haul international flights have been secured. Additionally, SkyQuest Airlines has enhanced its whistleblower protection program and established a dedicated department for managing regulatory risks in response to identified financial risks.

In summary, SKYQUEST AIRLINES is an aviation company committed to governance excellence, ethical practices, transparency, accountability, sustainability, social responsibility, and risk management while striving for long-term growth and profitability.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-33ee192d212baa53266387a4037c9551&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd92f011f39d6cf79cc64628733904f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbec5ba3239ce1a4bddeb2594eee98f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-684fc84c76b75a9c3f8bc82f55b02f9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-766dbb9c96afcb8af9cc0f61fd93fee4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345679b6578c022ea7e352f0eef3b332&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8770884a4ec114b8d262c5814fea2efc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09bd46ca13b030e394724af6ad225515&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4de161f310e17cacfcbe9539ec551381&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-970b353ef66299c02d01111d46c5bb8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2d9cd1f0d0f5c88cc1b20fb7c1e34f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-419a53615e44d16953003123ffe645b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41acd2a4f48bcb71253c95750bab07c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-863c15388fafeb22648afca453c45ce2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7051e2b1b19a9c618bf4a45b3972104b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ac872eaf5ffca549c7f180becdb7695&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae70c39276f969fcbc513317b8094c09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8580a095d1f53b1541822bcf720b4f80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f86303cacfe4151f25337e4c91342f71&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04d70fee668629a6b7563d565ad04a14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-464d603bd01b0a60bd9608fdf78e2b50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b4529c5f071f63d611b81d5299fc5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a359cee855fa7957394666df3b98f2b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c37d7c03f7e77b680013fdb3f1e9e59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4258f68a5bf81ba0bfea5865575b7cb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-533e006db8ed6844d09794ddf0a4d52b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-196d87ce26b956ddebef1c65f27d0956&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-10120249efe1ac9e462ace70eebafd83&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e26a32586ba157be5e0cdb82379e844d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad795281e3acace43f505e1dfbe9fc49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a66bc709ced931af221b43ae334d90d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c332d58d35f742c63c99c077d35ca4a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0dde0c570aca342a5d5a889bee23df08</data>
